OL,3,CStarmer criticises 'unacceptable'
OL,4,Ccondition of Labour MP's rental
OL,5,Cproperties
OL,7,FThe state of properties owned by
OL,8,FLabour MP Jas Athwal is
OL,9,F"unacceptable", Sir Keir Starmer said.
OL,11,FThe Prime Minister said it was "not
OL,12,Fgood enough" for the MP to allow
OL,13,Ftenants to live in flats infested with
OL,14,Fants and with black mould on the walls.
OL,16,FSir Keir said Mr Athwal had to take
OL,17,Faction to put it right "as quickly as
OL,18,Fpossible".
