OL,3,CStarmer criticises 'unacceptable'
OL,4,Ccondition of Labour MP's rental
OL,5,Cproperties
OL,7,FMr Athwal, the MP for Ilford South in
OL,8,Feast London, owns a rental portfolio
OL,9,Fincluding 15 residential and three
OL,10,Fcommercial properties in the capital,
OL,11,Faccording to Parliament's register of
OL,12,FMPs' interests.
OL,14,FA BBC investigation found black mould
OL,15,Fin some of the properties, with dirty
OL,16,Fand dark communal areas, fire alarms
OL,17,Fhanging loose from the ceiling, and
OL,18,Fant infestations in a number of the
OL,19,Fseven flats in one block.
