OL,3,CStarmer criticises 'unacceptable'
OL,4,Ccondition of Labour MP's rental
OL,5,Cproperties
OL,7,FSir Keir said: "It's unacceptable for
OL,8,Fany landlord, and I'll be really clear
OL,9,Fabout that it doesn't matter whether
OL,10,Fit's a Labour MP or anybody else, it's
OL,11,Funacceptable.
OL,13,F"What's happened in this case is this
OL,14,FMP has now recognised that, is taking
OL,15,Fthe necessary measures to put it right.
OL,17,F"The sooner that's done, the better,
OL,18,Fbut I'm not going to pretend to you or
OL,19,Fanybody else that this is in any way
OL,20,Facceptable."
