OL,3,CStarmer criticises 'unacceptable'
OL,4,Ccondition of Labour MP's rental
OL,5,Cproperties
OL,7,FAsked if he would strip the Labour
OL,8,Fwhip from the MP if the problems were
OL,9,Fnot resolved, Sir Keir said: "It has
OL,10,Fto be put right. He's taking action to
OL,11,Fput it right, we need to do that as
OL,12,Fquickly as possible."
OL,14,FMr Athwal has dismissed the agent
OL,15,Fresponsible for managing the
OL,16,Fproperties, saying he was "shocked and
OL,17,Fsickened" by the series of problems
OL,18,Fand "furious" not to have been made
OL,19,Faware of them earlier.
