OL,7,FIn a statement posted online on
OL,8,FSunday, Mr Athwal said: "As the
OL,9,Flandlord, the buck stops with me, and
OL,10,FI unreservedly apologise to my tenants
OL,11,Ffor the unacceptable experiences they
OL,12,Fhave endured.
OL,14,F"I will be reimbursing every tenant
OL,15,Fthat is out of pocket for repairs or
OL,16,Frenewals they have had to undertake.
