OL,7,F"I will be conducting a survey of my
OL,8,Ftenants, so that all issues are
OL,9,Funcovered and I am confident each one
OL,10,Fis living in secure, comfortable
OL,11,Fhomes."
OL,13,FAccording to the register of
OL,14,Finterests, Mr Athwal's rental
OL,15,Fproperties are "co-owned with (a)
OL,16,Ffamily member".
